{"id":104,"count":2,"description":"For thrill-seekers and nature lovers, our Special Adventure Tours are designed to get your adrenaline pumping while exploring India\u2019s most exciting landscapes. From trekking in the snow-capped Himalayas and river rafting in Rishikesh, to desert safaris in Rajasthan and scuba diving in the Andamans, these tours bring together the perfect mix of adventure, nature, and culture. Explore dense jungles on wildlife safaris, camp under starry skies, enjoy paragliding in Manali, or cycle through scenic trails in Kerala. Each experience is carefully curated for safety and excitement, with professional guides and quality equipment. Whether you\u2019re a beginner or a seasoned adventurer, our tours promise unforgettable memories and the thrill of discovering India from a whole new perspective.","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/destinations\/special-adventure-tours\/","name":"SPECIAL ADVENTURE TOURS","slug":"special-adventure-tours","taxonomy":"destination","parent":0,"meta":[],"thumbnail":{"width":900,"height":596,"file":"2025\/09\/SPECIAL-ADVENTURE-TOURS-.png","filesize":1052929,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"SPECIAL-ADVENTURE-TOURS--300x199.png","width":300,"height":199,"filesize":34316,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/SPECIAL-ADVENTURE-TOURS--300x199.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"SPECIAL-ADVENTURE-TOURS--150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":16323,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/SPECIAL-ADVENTURE-TOURS--150x150.png"},"medium_large":{"file":"SPECIAL-ADVENTURE-TOURS--768x509.png","width":768,"height":509,"filesize":132068,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/SPECIAL-ADVENTURE-TOURS--768x509.png"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"SPECIAL-ADVENTURE-TOURS--374x226.png","width":374,"height":226,"filesize":43800,"